snippet.textDisplay: My heartiest congratulations to everyone who invested such creativity and hard work to bring this masterpiece to life. This is more than an epic rendition of Assamese music, being also an eclectic kaleidoscope depicting everything an Assamese holds close to heart. Watching this made me tear up in admiration. Superb!!!!
